                        <interp inst="t18410405-name-949" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>THOMAS HANSON</persName>
                  </hi>. I live at Hounslow. I was in the tap-room, it the Wellington, and saw the prisoner—I bought the handkerchief and stockings of him for 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I saw him sell the candlestick and shell—he said he was in distress—I saw the prosecutor bring the prisoner in, and I gave up the property.</p>
