               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">CHARLES JENKS</hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant T</hi> 20.) I was on duty, and took him in charge.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I found the bundle just outside the public-house door, and I brought it in; I showed it to the landlord, and said, "Is this jour candlestick?" He said, "No" I took it into the tap-room, and could not get any body to own it; I then tried to sell it.</p>
